制，咁等咩50年呀<br />\n<br />\n咁融合，一國兩制同爭取民主，呢班仆街一定係會選擇融合<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a719a06fc885eeb0e1a1b433d9b846f6de406362","tid":1028381,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"275be66d3fc4269623038ce15618d452fe437a8d","tid":1028381,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T13:49:08.000Z","msg":"好波, 今次一定會全家投民主黨<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T13:58:07.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">一票不投<del>黃毓</del>民主黨</span></span>"},{"pid":"da012d695b8dfbedb7fb77e315cf6f63118b4615","tid":1028381,"uid":191926,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T13:58:17.000Z","msg":"又係胡志偉條成日扮智者的撚樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n最記得佢問港獨點搞 點做<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n心諗你個民主大中華又有咩步驟<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd831020a671e47af72e021dc3bcbb81a4fddf80","tid":1028381,"uid":104804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T14:07:17.000Z","msg":"有一點佢又岩<br />\n好多人大陸做生意<br />\n大陸生活<br />\n不過用香港人身份拿著數"},{"pid":"faef0159ba088eca72b69d39448d0f73d6f3c03a","tid":1028381,"uid":131157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T14:26:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"323ecf144c8d46f7ddd8f98520b2f0b816a394e8","tid":1028381,"uid":20725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T17:15:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 垃L圾"},{"pid":"6999e42da4ecf0f79409989ec3e630a1515e2006","tid":1028381,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-14T02:07:32.000Z","msg":"."},{"pid":"52dd261a0d744b441c674034d763e08cbfb8db13","tid":1028381,"uid":51701,"